  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Tower</b> may refer to:\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Characters\">Characters</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tower&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Characters\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hightower\" title=\"House Hightower\">House Hightower</a>, a noble family in the Reach</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Towers_(north)\" title=\"House Towers (north)\">House Towers</a>, a noble family in the North</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Towers_of_Harrenhal\" title=\"House Towers of Harrenhal\">House Towers</a>, a noble family in the Riverlands</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tyanna_of_the_Tower\" title=\"Tyanna of the Tower\">Tyanna of the Tower</a>, a queen of King Maegor I Targaryen</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Uthor_of_the_High_Tower\" title=\"Uthor of the High Tower\">Uthor of the High Tower</a>, the founder of House Hightower</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Locations\">Locations</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tower&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Locations\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Gull_Tower\" title=\"Gull Tower\">Gull Tower</a>, the seat of a brnach of House Shett</li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Hightower\" title=\"Hightower\">Hightower</a>, the seat of House Hightower</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Shadow_Tower\" title=\"Shadow Tower\">Shadow Tower</a>, a castle along the Wall</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ten_Towers\" title=\"Ten Towers\">Ten Towers</a>, the seat of House Harlaw</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Three_Towers\" title=\"Three Towers\">Three Towers</a>, the seat of House Costayne</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tower_of_Glimmering\" title=\"Tower of Glimmering\">Tower of Glimmering</a>, the seat of a cadet branch of House Harlaw</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tower_of_joy\" title=\"Tower of joy\">Tower of joy</a>, a watch tower in the Prince's Pass</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tumbledown_Tower\" title=\"Tumbledown Tower\">Tumbledown Tower</a>, a watchtower in the wolfswood</li></ul>\n<p>Named towers in castles:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Castle_Black\" title=\"Castle Black\">Castle Black</a>: <a href=\"/index.php/Hardin%27s_Tower\" title=\"Hardin&#39;s Tower\">Hardin's Tower</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Commander%27s_Tower\" title=\"Lord Commander&#39;s Tower\">Lord Commander's Tower</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Tower\" title=\"King&#39;s Tower\">King's Tower</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Lance_(tower)\" title=\"Lance (tower)\">Lance</a>, the Tower of Guards, the Silent Tower</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a>: <a href=\"/index.php/Stone_Drum\" title=\"Stone Drum\">Stone Drum</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Sea_Dragon_Tower\" title=\"Sea Dragon Tower\">Sea Dragon Tower</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Eyrie\" title=\"Eyrie\">Eyrie</a>: seven towers including the <a href=\"/index.php/Maiden%27s_Tower\" title=\"Maiden&#39;s Tower\">Maiden's Tower</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Moon_Tower\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Moon Tower\">Moon Tower</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Gates_of_the_Moon\" title=\"Gates of the Moon\">Gates of the Moon</a>: four square towers including the East Tower and the Falcon Tower</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a>: <a href=\"/index.php/Kingspyre_Tower\" title=\"Kingspyre Tower\">Kingspyre Tower</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Tower_of_Dread\" title=\"Tower of Dread\">Tower of Dread</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Tower_of_Ghosts\" title=\"Tower of Ghosts\">Tower of Ghosts</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Wailing_Tower\" title=\"Wailing Tower\">Wailing Tower</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Widow%27s_Tower\" title=\"Widow&#39;s Tower\">Widow's Tower</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mistwood\" title=\"Mistwood\">Mistwood</a>: <a href=\"/index.php/Tower_of_Owls\" title=\"Tower of Owls\">Tower of Owls</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Maidenpool\" title=\"Maidenpool\">Maidenpool</a>: Jonquil's Tower</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Moat_Cailin\" title=\"Moat Cailin\">Moat Cailin</a>: <a href=\"/index.php/Children%27s_Tower\" title=\"Children&#39;s Tower\">Children's Tower</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Drunkard%27s_Tower\" title=\"Drunkard&#39;s Tower\">Drunkard's Tower</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Gatehouse_Tower\" title=\"Gatehouse Tower\">Gatehouse Tower</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Nightsong\" title=\"Nightsong\">Nightsong</a>: Singing Towers</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a>: <a href=\"/index.php/Tower_of_the_Hand\" title=\"Tower of the Hand\">Tower of the Hand</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/White_Sword_Tower\" title=\"White Sword Tower\">White Sword Tower</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a>: Wheel Tower</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Sisterton\" title=\"Sisterton\">Sisterton</a>: <a href=\"/index.php/Night_Lamp\" title=\"Night Lamp\">Night Lamp</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Sunspear\" title=\"Sunspear\">Sunspear</a>: Tower of the Sun and Spear Tower</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ten_Towers\" title=\"Ten Towers\">Ten Towers</a>: Book Tower and Widow's Tower</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Twins\" title=\"Twins\">Twins</a>: Water Tower</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>: Broken/Burned Tower, Bell Tower, Library Tower</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Others\">Others</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tower&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Others\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Lady_of_the_Tower\" title=\"Lady of the Tower\">Lady of the Tower</a></i>, a war galley in the service of House Hightower</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Talking_Trees\" title=\"Talking Trees\">Talking Trees</a>, sometimes refer to as \"tower trees\".</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_40\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 40\">The Princess in the Tower</a>, the last Arianne POV chapter in <i>A Feast for Crows</i></li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404140618\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.007 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.008 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 11/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 16/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:36761-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404140618 and revision id 306358\n -->\n",
